data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER - UPDATED HOME: It's the perfect retreat for families seeking comfort and style, with four spacious bedrooms and two beautifully updated bathrooms. Step onto new flooring that adds a touch of sophistication and ensures durability and easy maintenance so you can enjoy your home without worry. The four generously sized bedrooms provide ample space to create your dream sanctuary for relaxation, work, or play. The kitchen is the heart of your home and is now a modern culinary paradise! It has been thoughtfully updated to provide a functional and beautiful space. The primary suite was updated with a new walk-in shower and an additional closet for extra storage. The backyard is a dream for those with kids and dogs, with plenty of space to run and play amongst the trees. The detached metal garage & shop are just what most shade mechanics have been looking for/ handy person. Enjoy gatherings at your new home with the covered deck and extra wide driveway,
